author: Kuokka77
description:
"Starfield Pheromone" by Interphace, 1st at Gerp 2024 chip music compo. This is also the soundtrack for "A Murder of Scrolls" demo, which ranked 2nd at Gerp 2024.
Atari ST/E art "The Sound of Silence" by Jade/SWEET16 etc., 1st at Sommarhack 2023 lowres gfx compo

A1200 r1D.4 audio. DeliTracker 2.34 with Paula-NotePlayer output (internal ProTracker replayer).
title: Amiga music: Interphace - Starfield Pheromone (A1200🎧Dolbyfied)
